{
  "stem": "27335.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somehow the-- well, we just-- then stood up and we went for another drink to-- to-- to the counter and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and somehow, just they came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just stepped closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a little balcony there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but after a few minutes, I could feel it, that she was an icicle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, she wasn't so easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Took a couple days in there, when our hands touched first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, probably the second or third-- third day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then slowly I-- I found that she was a really solid, determined-- determined girl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then-- then, as-- as we-- we went along-- we went along, then-- then I discovered he was-- in-- in some sense, she was too eager, too-- too anxious, and too-- and because of that, irresponsible.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was-- she was so, so eager to go, to go, to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her-- her life, her-- her whole manner, always-- always, always disciplined, disciplined as soldier.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then slowly I-- I begin to discovered-- well, you talked about Canada, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I told her that the whole story, of where I was, that we-- we-- we had-- we have Canada, we have Hungarian organization.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And indicated to her that-- that to the left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I was sure that I'm talking to the right-- right person, and that the Jewish organizations in-- in-- in Canada, same kind of leftist organization.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then-- then she began to talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh see that-- felt it coming closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
